        <updateDate>2020-11-03T15:31:42Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Preventing SBA Assistance from Going to China Act </b> </p> <p>This bill prohibits the Small Business Administration from providing aid, counsel, or assistance to a small business concern that (1) is headquartered in China, or (2) has more than 25% of voting stock owned by citizens of China. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
